{"tid":2028972,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民陣：一定奮力而戰 當我哋公佈行動 希望人數要多過 200 萬","createTime":"2020-05-22T04:57:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-23T12:02:25.000Z","uid":125168,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e749dd414f30cf5816f6c3bab564ef28e8fdca0a","tid":2028972,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T04:57:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0wtWv19.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0wtWv19.jpg&h=17b99184&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n民陣當年成立的關鍵，是 23 條立法。<br />\n國安法殺到，民陣一定奮力而戰。<br />\n<br />\n誠然，現在發起任何行動都非常困難。但 50 萬人頂住了 23 條，200 萬人與手足們各自爬山的努力頂住了送中惡法。我們暫時未能公佈行動細節，但我想同香港人講，無論你是黃絲還是藍絲，為了香港的人權民主自由法治、甚至只是你的飯碗，你都應該要站出來。<br />\n<br />\n希望當民陣公佈行動時，<br />\n我們的人數要多過 200 萬，<br />\n這樣我們會見到希望。<br />\n<br />\n香港，需要大家一齊救。<br />\n<br />\n【全文】 <a href=\"https://bit.ly/3cU08v3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3cU08v3&d=ppuFFh6piFuOrul45s7Bzctxnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=d4683551\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3cU08v3</a><br />\n【民陣、民主派記招片段】 youtu.be/nckiuOTDlpc<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/CivilHumanRightsFront/3097\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FCivilHumanRightsFront%2F3097&d=ppuFFh6piFuOrul45s7Bzctxnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=f02cfdfc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/CivilHumanRightsFront/3097</a>"},{"pid":"987b2144ace8d67b0c71a36e2a9f982d238b078b","tid":2028972,"uid":283912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T04:58:42.000Z","msg":"幾時公佈阿屌<br />\n一個星期後立仲等71？<br />\n<br />\n幫手叫雞524啦"},{"pid":"aecbd7f420da896adf56c9e81b04f1f22ac84e37","tid":2028972,"uid":262557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T05:01:39.000Z","msg":"快<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b5f6be1b6443175533f240dd620671259122f34","tid":2028972,"uid":146535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r